_source.text: [0344] According to the present invention, a rubber composition for forming a side wall of a tire, which can suppress a used amount of a component derived from a petroleum source, and is better in processability at unvulcanization and can suppress reduction in a rubber strength after thermal aging after vulcanization, as well as a side wall and a tire formed using the rubber composition can be provided.
